‌  def rows: Seq[RowResult]

  override def toString: String = {
    s"""

}

‌case class HeuristicResult(name: String,
                           results: Seq[AnalysisResult]) {
  override def toString: String = {
    s"""
      |$name
      |=============
      |${results.mkString("")}
      |""".stripMargin
  }
}

‌case class SimpleRowResult(name: String,
